              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Required Documentation Checklist</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Gather these essential documents before applying: government-issued photo ID, proof of income (recent pay stubs or benefit letters), and documentation showing participation in qualifying assistance programs.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                Applications move faster when you have everything ready. Missing paperwork is the most common reason for delays in getting your <strong>Free Government Phone</strong> approved and shipped.
              </p>
            </div>

